  "detailed_description": "<h1>More from HandyGames</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/771700/extras/640a75c87ef8bb319fa48b9ba0237554.avif?t=1771923533\" width=616 height=200 /></span></p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/771700/extras/66fa924fb74d3c4f4d7ada47cf9e1ca6.poster.avif?t=1771923533\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/771700/extras/66fa924fb74d3c4f4d7ada47cf9e1ca6.webm?t=1771923533\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/771700/extras/66fa924fb74d3c4f4d7ada47cf9e1ca6.mp4?t=1771923533\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Airhead is an adventure through a sprawling interconnected world, where you must explore, evolve and overcome intricate puzzles to succeed.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You play as Body, a small creature who meets a round, inflated organism and uses it as a head. And while Head is slowly but surely deflating, you have a chance to save its life.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >To do so, you need to use air cylinders to keep Head inflated while you explore Airhead’s interconnected world and learn about its secrets.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >On your adventure, it will be up to you to uncover the true connection between Head, the air cylinders, and the technology that litters the world so that you can save Head no matter the cost.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/771700/extras/4d88b022aad321e2cfcf8eb26bf08269.poster.avif?t=1771923533\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/771700/extras/4d88b022aad321e2cfcf8eb26bf08269.webm?t=1771923533\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/771700/extras/4d88b022aad321e2cfcf8eb26bf08269.mp4?t=1771923533\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/771700/extras/9042b441ccfb50c0d329ea414dcba6b8.avif?t=1771923533\" width=596 height=70 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Finding your way through Airhead's world is not always easy. You must brave dark caverns, ancient structures, and other mysterious locations in order to save Head.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Along the way, you will find new abilities, and uncover new areas and puzzles, and if you go even farther afield, who knows what hidden truths you may stumble upon?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/771700/extras/e998c081a35d719b5cced371628a6dc4.avif?t=1771923533\" width=596 height=70 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As you explore, you will encounter numerous puzzles involving the environment, strange creatures, and old technology to challenge your logic and creativity.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Everything is there for a reason and can be overcome by piecing together the puzzle and understanding the rules of Airhead's strange world. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/771700/extras/3cab3be56d8c259d013e947d75b06d97.avif?t=1771923533\" width=596 height=70 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Body and Head must work together to accomplish their goal, and as time passes, their bond and abilities will grow. What will you do to preserve their companionship?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >And when the impact of your choices becomes clear, are you willing to shoulder the consequences of saving a friend?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/771700/extras/82586b725f30af5ae307ab199093c9b1.poster.avif?t=1771923533\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/771700/extras/82586b725f30af5ae307ab199093c9b1.webm?t=1771923533\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/771700/extras/82586b725f30af5ae307ab199093c9b1.mp4?t=1771923533\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A beautiful art style, embracing bold colors and bleak shadows.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >An immersive 2.5D platformer experience. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Exploration in a mysterious world, filled with secrets and hidden paths.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Challenging puzzles, exploring the unique mechanics of a detachable head full of air.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Many powerful abilities to discover, each giving access to new areas and puzzles. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A personal story of companionship, discovery, and responsibility. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A myriad of creatures and machines to hinder and help you on your adventure.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A library filled with background information about Airhead's world and its inhabitants.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A ton of collectibles and even very hidden secret endings to uncover.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/771700/extras/58e5883e946000eaea67cb0a97e5efbe.avif?t=1771923533\" width=600 height=338 /></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/771700/extras/66fa924fb74d3c4f4d7ada47cf9e1ca6.poster.avif?t=1771923533\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/771700/extras/66fa924fb74d3c4f4d7ada47cf9e1ca6.webm?t=1771923533\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/771700/extras/66fa924fb74d3c4f4d7ada47cf9e1ca6.mp4?t=1771923533\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Airhead is an adventure through a sprawling interconnected world, where you must explore, evolve and overcome intricate puzzles to succeed.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You play as Body, a small creature who meets a round, inflated organism and uses it as a head. And while Head is slowly but surely deflating, you have a chance to save its life.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >To do so, you need to use air cylinders to keep Head inflated while you explore Airhead’s interconnected world and learn about its secrets.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >On your adventure, it will be up to you to uncover the true connection between Head, the air cylinders, and the technology that litters the world so that you can save Head no matter the cost.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/771700/extras/4d88b022aad321e2cfcf8eb26bf08269.poster.avif?t=1771923533\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/771700/extras/4d88b022aad321